Not all who wander are lost...
Unless you’re in Venice, then you’re definitely lost. 
We toured Rome til’ we dropped, saw beautiful Christmas decorations light up Florence, and splashed around Venice. 
Thanks for making this the best adventure yet <3

As hard as it is to handle, I find peace and beauty in you and Poppy leaving your earthly bodies together. The list of things that remind me of you is endless. You will be with me always and I know I’ve got two angels looking out for me. Thanks for always believing in me. I love you more than the sky, Babe.

I love you so much, Poppy. 
I’ll make sure to bring some Wheaties when we meet again ❤️
